title: EYL #196 Real Estate Fix and Flip Investing with Beyond Wynn

description:
In this episode we spoke to the Midwest real estate investing legend Beyond Wynn. We covered fix and flip real estate properties, rules to real estate, we talked about the Cleveland real estate market, best practices for out-of-state investors, and more. #realestate #investing #cleveland
